{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think it was after that that she decided that it wasn't safe enough to be around as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with the help of her lover, who was a Christian, I believe, she got false papers for us and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she faked, she left a suicide note.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She left most of her possessions there so that the neighbors wouldn't give us away, in essence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went to another suburb of Hungary, it was called [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from that time on, I was not allowed to be with other people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember being alone in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And to pacify me, mother got me two cats so I'd have something to play with.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she had hated cats up till then, but she grew to love them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And these cats were our companions right through, through the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in any case, I could not go out and be with people anymore because the situation was so dangerous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that I think I perceived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I knew that this-- we were now in a really dangerous times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, she was giving language lessons, because she had to support herself-- private language lessons, nothing public.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think there must have been a very short time between the time I returned from the village to the time that we got this false paper situation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was this painter's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Szekely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think his first name was Istvan, which means Steven.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we moved to a different apartment than the one where I remember playing with the cats.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, the neighbors [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] would question me about why I called him by his first name.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
